The legacy multi-page UI that used to live here has been removed —
the React SPA at /app/ (react/) is now the only frontend. See
nginx/nginx.conf (root `/` redirects to /app/) and react/PROTO.md.
Kept as an empty directory (Docker's `COPY static/` in nginx/Dockerfile
needs the source path to exist) rather than removed from the Dockerfile,
in case a future static asset (favicon, robots.txt) needs this path again.
